[Release Notes]
Armin van Buuren is the soul and pride of the Dutch dance music scene. In
2007 he was awarded the coveted number 1 position as "DJ of the world" by
readers of the British music magazine "DJ Mag". 2008 has also brought him
fame and good fortune, being the winner of the prestigious Dutch Pop
Prize. Currently he is getting ready for his third "Armin Only" concert.
The previous two editions were held in the Ahoy in Rotterdam, but this
year on Saturday April 19th all eyes will be on the man himself as he
takes his place behind the decks at the Jaarbeurs in Utrecht, playing to
more than 15,000 dance fans. The theme of this years Armin Only will be
"Imagine", the same title of his soon to be released album that he has
labored on for these past two years.
